              /li.fontsize-smaller.alt-link.u-marginbottom-10
                /a.alt-link href="http://juntoscomvc.uservoice.com/knowledgebase/articles/488683-sugest%C3%B5es-de-recompensas" target="_blank"  Sugestões de recompensas
              /li.fontsize-smaller.alt-link.u-marginbottom-10
                /a.alt-link href="http://juntoscomvc.uservoice.com/knowledgebase/articles/488680-recomenda%C3%A7%C3%B5es-do-juntos-com-vc" target="_blank"  Recomendações da Juntos.com.vc
          /.w-hidden-small.w-hidden-tiny.card.u-radius.u-marginbottom-20 data-ix="new-interaction"
            /.fontsize-small.fontweight-semibold.u-marginbottom-20 Suporte
            /ul.w-list-unstyled
              /li.alt-link.fontsize-smaller.u-marginbottom-10
                /a.alt-link href="http://juntoscomvc.uservoice.com/knowledgebase/articles/488678-como-a-juntos-com-vc-funciona" target="_blank"  Como a Juntos.com.vc funciona?
              /li.alt-link.fontsize-smaller.u-marginbottom-10
